       true,
       "inspect.getmembers.__class__.__name__.__eq__('function') == True — getmembers is a Python function defined in Lib/inspect.py; it returns all the members of an object in a list of (name, value) pairs; __class__.__name__ is 'function'; str.__eq__('function') returns True; new to extra148"]
    - [getmembers_qualname_eq,
       "getmembers.__qualname__.__eq__",
